kid-friendly meal for the kids with a simple twist. Sweet chilli is an all-time favourite flavour combo, turn it into a glaze and slather it
over pork rissoles for a tasty dinner. Reserve a portion and transform this dish into something new for the kids by adding fluffy rice!

